   "source": [
    "# Panacea — GRPO Oversight Agent Training\n",
    "**Model:** Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct + LoRA (4-bit)  \n",
    "**Method:** GRPO (no critic network — stable on T4)  \n",
    "**Task:** Detect fraud/deception in hospital resource claims  \n",
    "\n",
    "> Runtime → T4 GPU. Runtime → Connect before running cells."
   ]
  },
  {
